148
00:12:06,019 --> 00:12:09,860
[SPEAKER_00] Rekli su da je to jaka upala i da je ono 100% boli.

149
00:12:09,860 --> 00:12:12,679
[SPEAKER_00] Operirali su me, ja mislim, šest dana nakon toga.

150
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:13,179
[SPEAKER_00] Cisto?

151
00:12:13,179 --> 00:12:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] Cisto, da je bila je skoro 7 centimetara velika.

152
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ju i jesam osjećala.

153
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] I tri mjeseca nakon što su mene operirali,

154
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] mama moja je završila u Petrovoj, u bolnici.

155
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:29,580
[SPEAKER_00] I operirali su endometriozu.

156
00:12:29,580 --> 00:12:32,320
[SPEAKER_00] Znači prije, nego što sam ja dobila diagnozu,

157
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] pojma nisam imala što je to.

158
00:12:34,139 --> 00:12:36,659
[SPEAKER_00] Nikoga nisam znala koju ima ništa.

159
00:12:36,659 --> 00:12:39,019
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi, eto, unutar obitelji,

160
00:12:39,019 --> 00:12:42,860
[SPEAKER_00] ono oba dvije u kratkom periodu to operirali,

161
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:46,899
[SPEAKER_00] s tim da je njena očito puno dulje bila aktivna,

162
00:12:46,899 --> 00:12:50,419
[SPEAKER_00] jer je imala jako puno priraslica na crijevima.

163
00:12:50,419 --> 00:12:56,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, evo, baš onako zanimljivo da genetika ima tu

164
00:12:56,399 --> 00:12:59,740
[SPEAKER_00] nekakvu ulogu, ali ne mora nužno biti uloga.

165
00:12:59,740 --> 00:13:04,279
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno postoji nekakav splet okolnosti

166
00:13:04,279 --> 00:13:06,019
[SPEAKER_00] koji može to aktivirati.

167
00:13:06,019 --> 00:13:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] Danas imamo uz genetiku,

168
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] jako puno znamo o epigenetici.

169
00:13:10,039 --> 00:13:13,419
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ono, nije sve u genima.

170
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto je i do nas, i do načina života, do prehrane,

171
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] do higijenesna, do bilo čega.

172
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:27,820
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, svi, ja volim reći da svi mi imamo nekakav falš gen.

173
00:13:27,820 --> 00:13:29,200
[SPEAKER_00] Moramo imat.

174
00:13:30,659 --> 00:13:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pogotovo ako gledamo kako su naše priješnje generacije,

175
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:38,259
[SPEAKER_00] naši predsi živjeli i ovo je nekako podneblje gdje je bilo

176
00:13:38,259 --> 00:13:42,399
[SPEAKER_00] i ratova, i siromaštva, i gladi, i stresa.

177
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to mora ostaviti trag na buduće generacije,

178
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] na genetskoj razini.

179
00:13:47,279 --> 00:13:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] I onda, zapravo, način na koji mi vodimo život,

180
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:54,779
[SPEAKER_00] kako se mi brinemo i o svom živčanom sustavu,

181
00:13:54,779 --> 00:14:00,279
[SPEAKER_00] o prehrani, o bilo čemu, o društvu u kojem se nalazimo,

182
00:14:00,279 --> 00:14:04,899
[SPEAKER_00] jako može utjecat na ekspresiju i manifestaciju nekih bolesti

183
00:14:04,899 --> 00:14:06,820
[SPEAKER_00] ili izostanak istih.

184
00:14:06,820 --> 00:14:11,740
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, evo, moje ono, po svemu što znam,

185
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] ima genetika ulogu, ali ne mora nužno biti genetika.

186
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:16,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mora nas odrediti.

187
00:14:16,740 --> 00:14:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, da.

188
00:14:17,559 --> 00:14:20,600
[SPEAKER_01] Spominjalo se endokrine disruptore, onda se tako kaže.

189
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,139
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

190
00:14:21,139 --> 00:14:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje su najzastupljeni?

191
00:14:25,059 --> 00:14:29,899
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, endokrine disruptori su generalno ono više manje svudje

192
00:14:29,899 --> 00:14:32,000
